bot.net
Class Packet

java.lang.Object
  bot.net.Packet

public class Packet
extends java.lang.Object

Packet is used to encapsulate data being passed between bot process. It also contains features to encode and decode chunks of data to be sent. Raw Packet is string encoded like so: (nodesending>nodereceiving :type*command;_data0_data1_etc...) .

Author:
Brady O'Brien
